=\"Wizard Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/e/e9/Wizard_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Wizard\" title=\"Wizard\">Wizard</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Hate\n</th>\n<td><span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Jas\" title=\"Jas\"><img alt=\"Jas Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/68/Jas_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Jas\" title=\"Jas\">Jas</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Leo\" title=\"Leo\"><img alt=\"Leo Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/3/3d/Leo_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Leo\" title=\"Leo\">Leo</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Penny\" title=\"Penny\"><img alt=\"Penny Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/bc/Penny_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Penny\" title=\"Penny\">Penny</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Sebastian\" title=\"Sebastian\"><img alt=\"Sebastian Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/6a/Sebastian_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Sebastian\" title=\"Sebastian\">Sebastian</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Vincent\" title=\"Vincent\"><img alt=\"Vincent Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/0/0b/Vincent_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Vincent\" title=\"Vincent\">Vincent</a></span>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Bundles\">Bundles</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Mead&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Bundles\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Mead is one of the options for the <span style=\"display:inline; margin-right:0;\"><img alt=\"Bundle Orange.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/95/Bundle_Orange.png/24px-Bundle_Orange.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/95/Bundle_Orange.png/36px-Bundle_Orange.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/9/95/Bundle_Orange.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Remixed_Bundles#Brewer.27s_Bundle\" title=\"Remixed Bundles\">Brewer's Bundle</a> in the <a href=\"/Remixed_Bundles#Pantry\" title=\"Remixed Bundles\">Pantry (Remixed)</a></span>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recipes\">Recipes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Mead&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Recipes\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Mead is not used in any recipes.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tailoring\">Tailoring</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Mead&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Tailoring\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Mead can be used in the spool of the <a href=\"/2_Willow_Lane#Sewing_Machine\" title=\"2 Willow Lane\">Sewing Machine</a> to create the <a href=\"/File:Shirt138.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Shirt138.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Shirt138.png/24px-Shirt138.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/e/e4/Shirt138.png 1.5x\" /></a> <a href=\"/Tailoring\" title=\"Tailoring\">Black Leather Jacket</a>. It can be used in <a href=\"/Dyeing\" title=\"Dyeing\">dyeing</a>, serving as a yellow dye at the dye pots, located in <a href=\"/Emily\" title=\"Emily\">Emily</a>'s and <a href=\"/Haley\" title=\"Haley\">Haley</a>'s house, <a href=\"/2_Willow_Lane\" title=\"2 Willow Lane\">2 Willow Lane</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quests\">Quests</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Mead&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Quests\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Mead is not used in any <a href=\"/Quests\" title=\"Quests\">quests</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Mead&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.1\" title=\"Version History\">1.1</a>: Introduced.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.4\" title=\"Version History\">1.4</a>: Can now be used in <a href=\"/Tailoring\" title=\"Tailoring\">Tailoring</a>. Now a hated gift for Sebastian, Jas, and Vincent.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.5\" title=\"Version History\">1.5</a>: Can be obtained from the bartender in the Ginger Island Pirate Cove. Is now an option in the Brewer's Bundle.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.6\" title=\"Version History\">1.6</a>: Base sell price increased from 200g to 300g. Parrot Egg now counts as pirate attire for the free Mead from the pirate bartender. Now purchasable at <a href=\"/Desert_Festival\" title=\"Desert Festival\">Desert Festival</a>.</li></ul>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" id=\"navbox\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Artisan_Goods\" title=\"Artisan Goods\">Artisan Goods</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Bee_House\" title=\"Bee House\">Bee House</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Honey\" title=\"Honey\">Honey</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Cask\" title=\"Cask\">Cask</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Beer\" title=\"Beer\">Beer</a> • <a href=\"/Cheese\" title=\"Cheese\">Cheese</a> • <a href=\"/Goat_Cheese\" title=\"Goat Cheese\">Goat Cheese</a> • <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mead</a> • <a href=\"/Pale_Ale\" title=\"Pale Ale\">Pale Ale</a> • <a href=\"/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">Wine</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Cheese_Press\" title=\"Cheese Press\">Cheese Press</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Cheese\" title=\"Cheese\">Cheese</a> • <a href=\"/Goat_Cheese\" title=\"Goat Cheese\">Goat Cheese</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Keg\" title=\"Keg\">Keg</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Beer\" title=\"Beer\">Beer</a> • <a href=\"/Coffee\" title=\"Coffee\">Coffee</a> • <a href=\"/Green_Tea\" title=\"Green Tea\">Green Tea</a> • <a href=\"/Juice\" title=\"Juice\">Juice</a> • <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mead</a> • <a href=\"/Pale_Ale\" title=\"Pale Ale\">Pale Ale</a> • <a href=\"/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">Wine</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Loom\" title=\"Loom\">Loom</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Cloth\" title=\"Cloth\">Cloth</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Mayonnaise_Machine\" title=\"Mayonnaise Machine\">Mayonnaise Machine</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Dinosaur_Mayonnaise\" title=\"Dinosaur Mayonnaise\">Dinosaur Mayonnaise</a> • <a href=\"/Duck_Mayonnaise\" title=\"Duck Mayonnaise\">Duck Mayonnaise</a> • <a href=\"/Mayonnaise\" title=\"Mayonnaise\">Mayonnaise</a> • <a href=\"/Void_Mayonnaise\" title=\"Void Mayonnaise\">Void Mayonnaise</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Oil_Maker\" title=\"Oil Maker\">Oil Maker</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Oil\" title=\"Oil\">Oil</a> • <a href=\"/Truffle_Oil\" title=\"Truffle Oil\">Truffle Oil</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Preserves_Jar\" title=\"Preserves Jar\">Preserves Jar</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Aged_Roe\" title=\"Aged Roe\">Aged Roe</a> • <a href=\"/Caviar\" title=\"Caviar\">Caviar</a> • <a href=\"/Jellies_and_Pickles\" title=\"Jellies and Pickles\">Jellies and Pickles</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Fish_Smoker\" title=\"Fish Smoker\">Fish Smoker</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Smoked_Fish\" title=\"Smoked Fish\">Smoked Fish</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Dehydrator\" title=\"Dehydrator\">Dehydrator</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Dried_Mushrooms\" title=\"Dried Mushrooms\">Dried Mushrooms</a> • <a href=\"/Dried_Fruit\" title=\"Dried Fruit\">Dried Fruit</a> • <a href=\"/Raisins\" title=\"Raisins\">Raisins</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Misc\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Maple_Syrup\" title=\"Maple Syrup\">Maple Syrup</a> • <a href=\"/Oak_Resin\" title=\"Oak Resin\">Oak Resin</a> • <a href=\"/Pine_Tar\" title=\"Pine Tar\">Pine Tar</a>  • <a href=\"/Mystic_Syrup\" title=\"Mystic Syrup\">Mystic Syrup</a>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260414110750\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.288 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.713 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 4181/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 81307/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 3507/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 17/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 11728/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.019/7.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 1.19 MB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  475.735      1 -total\n 83.20%  395.829      1 Template:Infobox\n 19.41%   92.321      1 Template:EdibilityGrid\n 17.62%   83.817      1 Template:Description\n 16.07%   76.467      4 Template:Name\n 11.71%   55.692      8 Template:Qualityprice\n 11.49%   54.684     20 Template:Overlayimg\n  5.74%   27.290      2 Template:Duration\n  4.80%   22.855      1 Template:GiftsByItem\n  3.65%   17.346      1 Template:Bundle\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:5780-0!canonical and timestamp 20260414110749 and revision id 190688\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": "{{Infobox\n|eng             = Mead\n|source          = <nowiki />\n*[[Artisan Goods]]\n*[[Ginger Island#Island South|Ginger Island Resort]]\n|buff            = {{Name|Tipsy|link=Buffs#Tipsy{{!}}Tipsy}}{{Name|Speed|−1}}\n|buffduration    = 30s\n|edibility       = 30\n|sellprice       = 300\n|ingredients     = {{Name|Honey|1}}\n|craftingstation = {{Name|Keg}}\n|crafttime       = 10h\n}}\n'''Mead''' is an [[Artisan Goods|Artisan Good]] made from placing [[Honey]] inside a [[Keg]], taking 10 hours. It is also available at the [[Ginger Island#Island South|Ginger Island Resort]] for {{Price|800}}. [[Pam]] sells Mead in her [[Desert Festival#Villager Shops|shop]] at the [[Desert Festival]] for {{Price|20|Calico}} [[Calico Egg]]s. Unlike [[Wine]] and [[Juice]] however, the value of the Mead is '''not''' affected by the type of honey used.  The sell price of Mead is {{Price|300}}, and only [[Cask|aging]] or the [[Skills#Farming|Artisan Profession]] can increase it. Several types of [[Honey#Sell Prices|Flower Honey]] sell for more than Mead, so the player can actually lose gold by making Mead.\n\nMead can also be obtained for free from the bar in the [[Ginger Island#Pirate Cove|Pirate Cove]] by speaking with the bartender while wearing the [[Pirate Hat]], [[Deluxe Pirate Hat]], [[Eye Patch]], or [[Parrot Egg]] trinket. This can only be done once per night.\n\nWhen consumed, Mead causes a [[Buffs|Tipsy]] buff that decreases [[Speed]] by 1.\n\n==Aged Values==\nMead can be placed inside a [[Cask]] to age from normal quality to silver, gold, and eventually iridium quality. Iridium quality doubles the base sell price of Mead.  \n\nNormal, silver, and gold quality Mead can be prematurely removed from a cask at any time by striking the cask with an [[Axes|Axe]], [[Hoes|Hoe]], or [[Pickaxes|Pickaxe]].\n\n{|class=\"wikitable roundedborder\"\n!Normal Quality\n!Silver Quality<br />(x 1.25)\n!Gold Quality<br />(x 1.5)\n!Iridium Quality<br />(x 2)\n|-\n|{{Qualityprice|Mead|300|quality=normal|dsv=false}}\n|{{Qualityprice|Mead|300|quality=silver|dsv=false}} ''Aged: 7 Days''\n|{{Qualityprice|Mead|300|quality=gold|dsv=false}} ''Aged: 7 Days<br />Total: 14 Days''\n|{{Qualityprice|Mead|300|quality=iridium|dsv=false}} ''Aged: 14 Days<br />Total: 28 Days''\n|-\n|}\n\n==Gifting==\n{{GiftsByItem\n|like=Robin,Demetrius,Maru,Linus,Pierre,Caroline,Abigail,Alex,George,Evelyn,Lewis,Clint,Emily,Haley,Jodi,Kent,Sam,Leah,Marnie,Elliott,Gus,Dwarf,Wizard,Harvey,Sandy,Krobus,Shane\n|hate=Jas,Penny,Sebastian,Vincent,Leo\n|love=Pam,Willy\n}}\n\n==Bundles==\nMead is one of the options for the {{Bundle|Brewers||y}}.\n\n==Recipes==\nMead is not used in any recipes.\n\n==Tailoring==\nMead can be used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the [[File:Shirt138.png|24px]] [[Tailoring|Black Leather Jacket]]. It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as a yellow dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].\n\n==Quests==\nMead is not used in any [[quests]].\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.1|Introduced.}}\n{{History|1.4|Can now be used in [[Tailoring]]. Now a hated gift for Sebastian, Jas, and Vincent.}}\n{{History|1.5|Can be obtained from the bartender in the Ginger Island Pirate Cove. Is now an option in the Brewer's Bundle.}}\n{{History|1.6|Base sell price increased from 200g to 300g. Parrot Egg now counts as pirate attire for the free Mead from the pirate bartender. Now purchasable at [[Desert Festival]].}}\n\n{{NavboxArtisanGoods}}\n\n[[Category:Artisan Goods]]\n\n[[de:Met]]\n[[es:Hidromiel]]\n[[fr:Hydromel]]\n[[it:Idromele]]\n[[ja:はちみつ酒]]\n[[ko:벌꿀 술]]\n[[hu:Mézsör]]\n[[pt:Hidromel]]\n[[ru:Медовуха]]\n[[tr:Likör]]\n[[zh:蜜蜂酒]]"
    }
